Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.50,0:02:33.60,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}然后呢 哈尔是什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.60,0:02:34.35,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.35,0:02:36.00,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}刚才人家不是这么叫你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.00,0:02:36.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.80,0:02:38.55,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你没发现吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.35,0:06:07.45,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没有人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.35,0:06:09.30,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这里也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.80,0:06:11.70,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好 上楼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.40,0:06:26.98,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}憎恨殷红
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.98,0:06:28.35,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.35,0:06:29.60,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}往上 一口气冲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.35,0:06:58.15,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}成功了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.15,0:06:59.55,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.90,0:07:11.90,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.00,0:07:31.75,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Exhaust!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.40,0:07:33.40,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.20,0:07:34.75,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.35,0:07:37.60,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}奇怪 为啥不追过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.60,0:07:39.30,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因为你太明显了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.65,0:07:43.15,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那群家伙很了解人类的战斗方式
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.15,0:07:47.00,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}欧姆雷尔·艾克类·威尔·达修
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.95,0:07:59.35,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也见识过魔法？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.55,0:08:05.85,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你竟敢伤害了梦儿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.60,0:08:14.05,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一个人很难挡住...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.05,0:08:15.05,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哈尔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.05,0:08:16.05,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}换我来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.65,0:08:41.40,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哈尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.10,0:08:43.10,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没...没事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.85,0:08:50.65,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}光啊 以路米艾里斯加护之名 治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.60,0:08:55.60,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.60,0:08:57.45,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}来这边帮忙 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.95,0:09:03.05,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这点小事...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.05,0:09:04.65,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}完全没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.65,0:09:06.85,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我 我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.85,0:09:08.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}感觉像变了个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.35,0:09:12.25,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}欧姆雷尔·艾克特·威尔·达修
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.55,0:09:22.60,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}光啊 以路米艾里斯加护之名 治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.65,0:09:32.65,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}欧姆雷尔·艾克特·威尔·达修
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.00,0:09:40.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.30,0:09:46.00,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}安格
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.65,0:09:49.30,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好勒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.30,0:09:50.60,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}别吓我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.20,0:09:53.95,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我...我想近点应该能打中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.95,0:09:55.20,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.00,0:09:57.15,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不过干得好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.95,0:10:00.90,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.40,0:10:04.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}让它们见识见识我们做的一切不是白费
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.25,0:10:24.65,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这都濒死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.80,0:10:30.85,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这可是关乎性命的搏斗 别恨我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.50,0:10:51.00,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}梅丽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.90,0:10:52.90,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.60,0:10:56.20,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}住手 你做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.20,0:10:59.10,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么能让梅丽像马纳多那样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.60,0:11:07.60,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:08.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}蓝德
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.05,0:11:13.05,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}成功了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.55,0:11:14.90,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你给我滚下来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.90,0:11:16.40,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}梅丽 梅丽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.40,0:11:17.15,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}梅丽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.65,0:11:22.15,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉 我能治疗一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.15,0:11:24.95,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有点...还挺疼的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.70,0:11:27.00,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}给我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.00,0:11:27.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.80,0:11:28.85,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那可是屋顶上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.85,0:11:29.85,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我的话能行动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.50,0:11:47.55,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那把短刀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.75,0:11:51.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.40,0:12:04.25,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哈尔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.45,0:12:19.45,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}谢谢 梦儿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.45,0:12:27.75,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.45,0:13:06.65,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我一直在思考...如果这个时刻到来了该说什么好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.10,0:13:17.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}总觉得好像相处了很久
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.75,0:13:20.00,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但却不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.20,0:13:24.00,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不如说 相处的时间不长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.45,0:13:26.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}非常短
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.50,0:13:31.40,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以好像了解 却又不了解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.80,0:13:37.85,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人很好 很亲切 头脑很灵活
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.15,0:13:41.00,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什么都会做 很值得依靠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.65,0:13:45.95,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我觉得他是个无懈可击的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.50,0:13:52.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是 可能只是我没有察觉到他的缺点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.10,0:13:56.05,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可能只是他隐藏了自己的弱点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.30,0:14:01.75,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果相处更久 说不定能发现他的另一面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.05,0:14:09.15,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真想知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.80,0:14:13.10,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想知道他其实是个什么样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.50,0:14:15.70,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想要在多一点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.95,0:14:20.35,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只要有时间 肯定会发生更多的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.55,0:14:27.05,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}说不定会互相看不顺眼 说不定还会吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.70,0:14:33.15,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}说不定会讨厌他 也说不定会更喜欢他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.70,0:14:38.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}马纳多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.65,0:14:41.20,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们成为义勇兵了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.55,0:14:57.20,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那时候 我们连团章都买不起 吃的东洗也都精打细算的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.55,0:15:04.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}连明天的住宿费都不知道付不付得起 内裤都买不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.60,0:15:08.10,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我可是干脆没穿内裤哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.00,0:15:10.85,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}现在穿了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.75,0:15:15.25,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这样的我们也正式成为了义勇兵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.00,0:15:19.25,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 倒不是说没钱买团章
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.20,0:15:24.00,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只是想做个了结 告一段落之后再买
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.15,0:15:26.47,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是大家一起决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.47,0:15:30.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哈 我倒是无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.50,0:15:32.10,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是因为你们太啰嗦了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.10,0:15:33.40,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}笨蛋蓝德
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.40,0:15:36.60,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这种时候就别说讨棱厌的话了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.20,0:15:39.40,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你本来就很讨厌来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.80,0:15:42.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}正合我意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.50,0:15:46.40,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我可是暗黑骑士啊 就应该被人讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.20,0:15:51.15,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是讨棱厌 是讨人厌 姑且说一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.95,0:15:55.00,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我...我说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.00,0:15:56.45,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}差不多该把那个拿出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.35,0:16:04.10,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是马纳多的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.80,0:16:12.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}用马纳多原本自己的钱买的 不够的大家一起出了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.35,0:16:16.10,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}梅丽小姐也出了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.40,0:16:19.60,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}请收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.30,0:16:39.35,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果你听到了 会不会笑着说不用这么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:45.35,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}说这样浪费钱 不如买点装备好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.65,0:16:53.35,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}虽然你说什么我们都不会改变主意的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.20,0:17:55.90,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们开始成为一支不错的队伍了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.35,0:19:17.60,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}梅丽 伤口没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.80,0:19:20.40,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我用魔法治好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.30,0:19:23.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这样啊 也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.40,0:19:26.30,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不过需要缝一下衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.20,0:19:28.40,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}开了个洞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.90,0:19:45.60,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要是衣服也能用魔法修好该多方便啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.80,0:19:47.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.80,0:20:08.35,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么了 哈尔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.10,0:20:10.65,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你看起来不是很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.40,0:20:13.35,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明明为同伴报了仇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.55,0:20:16.00,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你这么叫我...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.30,0:20:18.40,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.25,0:20:20.40,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你不喜欢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.40,0:20:22.35,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.30,0:20:26.15,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因为我没怎么被这么叫过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.55,0:20:30.20,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.55,0:20:32.15,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.35,0:20:41.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯...那个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.80,0:20:47.10,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}虽然衣服也要自己缝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.05,0:20:53.05,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是难受的心情用魔法也是治不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.05,0:20:54.85,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这就是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.55,0:20:56.55,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我刚才所想的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.85,0:21:05.85,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}失去马纳多一个人 我们就已经这么难过了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.40,0:21:13.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那个...梅丽你不是失去了三个同伴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.20,0:21:16.90,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}然后我就想...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.40,0:21:20.60,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}原来你知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.80,0:21:22.55,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.80,0:21:25.70,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你不想听这种事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.15,0:21:34.00,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊...我...真的对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.85,0:21:37.75,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.50,0:21:44.00,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想确实有魔法治愈不了的伤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.30,0:21:46.05,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.35,0:21:56.95,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是听哈尔这么说 虽然难受
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.75,0:21:58.85,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但并不讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.65,0:22:00.65,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这点你要搞清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.00,0:22:04.70,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}梅丽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.50,0:22:06.10,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.80,0:22:34.20,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.10,0:22:37.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.70,0:22:52.40,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.40,0:22:54.40,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明天见
